Capabilities a software developer should probably have:
- Working with a cloud based version control system.
- Ability to create write a simple server.
- Ability to deploy a server on the cloud.
- Ability to create a simple dynamic webpage.
- Ability to work with databases.
- Understanding a logging framework.
- Build tool like maven.
- Basic knowledge of Java (installation, classpath, etc.)
- Testing (principles and technique)
- Debugging
